          <section id="arch-pipeline" class="docs-section">
            <h3>Data Pipeline</h3>
            <pre class="docs-pre"><code>COURSE CREATION
  course.md edited → PR opened
    └─ validate-pr.yml: parse + tamper-check → PR comment report
  PR merged to main
    └─ course-publish.yml:
         Job 1 validate: parse-course.ts → course.json (per-course)
         Job 2 detect-contributors: detect-contributors.ts → contributors.json (per-course)
         Job 3 (dispatch): sync-site-data.yml →
           sync-site-data.ts:
             reads  engine/courses/*/course.json
             reads  engine/courses/*/contributors.json
             fetches GitHub API (stars, forks, commit activity)
             writes site/src/data/courses.json
             writes site/src/data/contributors.json
             writes site/src/data/activity.json
             writes site/src/data/graph.json
             writes site/src/data/changelog.json
             writes site/src/data/stats.json
           commits site/src/data/* → triggers deploy-site.yml
    └─ deploy-site.yml: bun run build → GitHub Pages artifact → deploy

ENROLLMENT & GRADING
  enrollment-request issue opened
    └─ enroll.yml → enroll.ts → relabel issue + welcome comment
  quiz-submit issue opened
    └─ run-quiz.yml → quiz-engine.ts → Docker sandbox (code Qs) → grade comment
       on pass: dispatches course-leaderboard.yml
  project-submit issue or PR
    └─ grade-assignment.yml → Docker sandbox → grade.ts → grade comment
       on pass: dispatches course-leaderboard.yml

LEADERBOARD
  course-leaderboard.yml (nightly 02:00 UTC or on quiz/project pass):
    leaderboard.ts → reads all enrolled issues → builds rankings
    writes engine/LEADERBOARD.md + site/src/data/leaderboard.json
    commits → deploy-site.yml rebuilds

MAINTENANCE
  check-links.yml (weekly Mon 04:00): check-links.ts → opens dead-link issue
  check-videos.yml (weekly Mon 06:00): validate-videos.ts → opens dead-video issue
  sync-site-data.yml (nightly 03:00): full data refresh even without course changes</code></pre>
          </section>

